Amy Dalby https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amy_Dalby 0 Amy Mary Dalby (1888 in Clerkenwell – 10 March 1969) was an English actress of stage and screen, often in kindly or eccentric spinster roles.Dalby's final performance was in the 8 March 1969 episode "The Battle of Godfrey's Cottage" of Dad's Army, portraying the sister of Private Godfrey. She died in London on 10 March — two days after the episode aired.
